Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那借来的写轮眼能抵挡这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识下真品与盗版的差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视线…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 她怎么过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让卡卡西老师背负一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走的不是一条道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:00:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起努力过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经认为那就是自己该走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是决意踏上复仇之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此我才活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法像你和鸣人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了佐助什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…求求你 留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想尽一切办法帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请你和我一起留下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果实在不行 就带我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然…很讨人厌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我就喊人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来的真是时候啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你能过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助真的打算杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果鸣人没有赶来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我已经被佐助亲手杀死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱同是第七班的成员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说是曾经的第七班…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 小樱 你们现在应该明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他身上浮现的是真正的杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经不是曾经的佐助了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼬的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听阿飞那家伙说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼬的真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道那家伙说的是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既没父母也没兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我的理解能有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外人给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道鸣人是怎么对你的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么流言蜚语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都一直视你为伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便大家都准备对付佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人还是一心想着救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么救…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对要把你…从复仇的泥泞中拯救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的复仇帷幕已经拉开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手刃了一个鼬的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到那只右手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀害了多少宇智波族人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出手的是鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你逼他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是里四象封印术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 快远离团藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这干掉了木叶的高层
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫团藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助难道仅凭一人就打倒他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止 从未有过的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被玷污的宇智波得到净化的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波从这腐朽的忍者世界超脱的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是无法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种意义上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是你们木叶长久以来的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你们所愿 让亘古以来一直被否定的宇智波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你们的记忆中消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩断同木叶所有的羁绊才是净化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是宇智波的真正复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那憎恨累积而成的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造就了现在的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助也是这个时代的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人也好 小樱也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽不能确定 但多少也能察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都给我离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 卡卡西老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在这里会看到不愿看到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 从静音那学来的毒苦无是杀不掉佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他继承了大蛇丸的免疫力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你已经清楚自己的心意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我已经帮你恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续战斗可不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动 香燐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同人质的要害一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 这是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罢了 佐助的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓不愿看到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杀了佐助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有破绽 我可不会手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 或许…我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该反过来才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断地逃啊 逃啊 苟且偷生下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后当有一天你拥有跟我相同的眼睛后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经被村民们厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为我体内的九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经也憎恨村里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也曾想过报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些涂鸦给我擦干净
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那小子 就是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要将这种家伙留在村子里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三代替我们想想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个混蛋 滚一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么突然来一下你要干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你好了 赶紧给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都这样对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连班主任也用这种眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是扫把星或霉菌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果稍有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会像你一样想着如此恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾觉得我会一直孤单下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到同你和伊鲁卡老师相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高次 回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大智 吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不听话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说过不准和那个孩子一起玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…告诉你真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道十二年前封印妖狐的事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后村里就有了条规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是条绝对不能让你知道的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只对我保密 什么规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能说出鸣人就是妖狐的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 你就是杀害了伊鲁卡的双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭村子的九尾妖狐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所憧憬的第四代火影将九尾封印在你体内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里所有人都瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会认同你这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果再可靠些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不会经历这些痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走火入魔般的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你和伊鲁卡老师 我才得救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我知道你也总是一人时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你跟我一样我就觉得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你都是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背负着九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背负着宇智波的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们背负着相似的包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天看到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实想去找你聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得你应该能理解我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问原因的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你什么都行 让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我决定把你当作我的竞争对手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那时起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就成了我的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾在终结之谷说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的对决让我终于有所理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也读懂我内心的真实想法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:22:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.91,0:23:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么对我如此执着
